## Risk Assessment

**Low Risk:**
- WeatherMap layout change (CSS Grid/Flexbox)
- Location input move (simple DOM change)
- Default size setting (one-line change)

**Medium Risk:**
- Drag-drop with Masonry (potential positioning conflicts)
- Forecast auto-fetch (performance impact)

**High Risk:**
- None (all changes are UI-only, no data model changes)

**Mitigation:**
- Test drag-drop thoroughly with different widget combinations
- Use `verticalListSortingStrategy` to avoid Masonry conflicts
- Lazy-load forecast data (fetch only when needed)

